{"meta":{"title":"Moroni 3","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/3?lang=spa","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ/2017-11-2320-moroni-03-64k-spa.mp3?download=true","voice":{"name":"audio"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"000c179d2450a467090a5d6da3557dfd207ffa30","data-aid":"124250084","data-aid-version":"3","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/3","itemscope":"","itemtype":"http://schema.org/Article","lang":"spa","data-orig-id":"d8eea313723aec5fb2100222f4e6778642ead1e4","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"Moroni 3","description":"Los élderes ordenan presbíteros y maestros mediante la imposición de manos. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"Moroni 3","description":"Los élderes ordenan presbíteros y maestros mediante la imposición de manos. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"124250326\" id=\"title_number1\">Capítulo 3</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"124250329\" id=\"study_summary1\">Los élderes ordenan presbíteros y maestros mediante la imposición de manos. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"627\"></span>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124250331\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>La forma en que los discípulos, que eran llamados los <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>élderes</a> de la iglesia, <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>ordenaban</a> presbíteros y maestros:</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124250334\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>Después de haber orado al Padre en el nombre de Cristo, les imponían las manos, y decían:</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124250336\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>En el nombre de Jesucristo, te ordeno para que seas presbítero (o si fuera maestro, te ordeno para que seas maestro) para predicar el arrepentimiento y la <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>remisión</a> de pecados, por medio de Jesucristo, mediante la perseverancia en la fe en su nombre hasta el fin. Amén.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124250337\" id=\"p4\"><span class=\"verse-number\">4 </span>Y de este modo <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>ordenaban</a> presbíteros y maestros, según los <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>dones</a> y llamamientos de Dios a los hombres; y los ordenaban por el <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>poder</a> del Espíritu Santo que había en ellos.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124250338\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/6.1?lang=spa#p1\">Alma 6:1</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/elder?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Élder (anciano)</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note1b\" data-full-marker=\"1b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124250339\" id=\"note1b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/ordain-ordination?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Ordenación, ordenar</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note3a\" data-full-marker=\"3a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124250340\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/remission-of-sins?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Remisión de pecados</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"4\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note4a\" data-full-marker=\"4a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124250341\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.32?lang=spa#p32\">DyC 18:32</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.60?lang=spa#p60\">20:60</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note4b\" data-full-marker=\"4b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124250342\" id=\"note4b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/gift?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Don</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note4c\" data-full-marker=\"4c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124250343\" id=\"note4c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/13.37?lang=spa#p37\">1 Ne. 13:37</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/6.9?lang=spa#p9\">Moro. 6:9</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note1a":{"id":"note1a","marker":"1a","pid":"124250331","context":"élderes","text":"<p data-aid=\"124250338\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/6.1?lang=spa#p1\">Alma 6:1</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/elder?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Élder (anciano)</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/6.1?lang=spa#p1","text":"Alma 6:1"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/elder?lang=spa","text":"GEE Élder (anciano)"}]},"note1b":{"id":"note1b","marker":"1b","pid":"124250331","context":"ordenaban","text":"<p data-aid=\"124250339\" id=\"note1b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/ordain-ordination?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Ordenación, ordenar</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/ordain-ordination?lang=spa","text":"GEE Ordenación, ordenar"}]},"note3a":{"id":"note3a","marker":"3a","pid":"124250336","context":"remisión","text":"<p data-aid=\"124250340\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/remission-of-sins?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Remisión de pecados</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/remission-of-sins?lang=spa","text":"GEE Remisión de pecados"}]},"note4a":{"id":"note4a","marker":"4a","pid":"124250337","context":"ordenaban","text":"<p data-aid=\"124250341\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.32?lang=spa#p32\">DyC 18:32</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.60?lang=spa#p60\">20:60</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.32?lang=spa#p32","text":"DyC 18:32"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.60?lang=spa#p60","text":"20:60"}]},"note4b":{"id":"note4b","marker":"4b","pid":"124250337","context":"dones","text":"<p data-aid=\"124250342\" id=\"note4b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/gift?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Don</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/gift?lang=spa","text":"GEE Don"}]},"note4c":{"id":"note4c","marker":"4c","pid":"124250337","context":"poder","text":"<p data-aid=\"124250343\" id=\"note4c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/13.37?lang=spa#p37\">1 Ne. 13:37</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/6.9?lang=spa#p9\">Moro. 6:9</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/13.37?lang=spa#p37","text":"1 Ne. 13:37"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/6.9?lang=spa#p9","text":"Moro. 6:9"}]}}},"pids":[["124250084",{"key":"124250084"}],["124250326",{"key":"124250326"}],["124250329",{"key"